t-dylan-bruce-adam-donner/|archive-date=October 5, 2013|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Bex Taylor-Klaus]] as [[Cindy Simone|Sin]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2013/08/15/arrow-bex-taylor-klaus-season-2-sin/|title=Arrow Scoop: Breakout Killing Co-Star Commits to 'Sin'-ful Season 2 Arc|first=Michael|last=Ausiello|work=tvline|date=August 15, 2013|accessdate=October 23, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020133953/http://tvline.com/2013/08/15/arrow-bex-taylor-klaus-season-2-sin/|archive-date=October 20, 2013|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Dylan Neal]] as [[Anthony Ivo (Arrowverse)|Anthony Ivo]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://screencrush.com/arrow-season-2-dr-anthony-ivo-dylan-neal-exclusive/|title=\u2018Arrow\u2019 Season 2 Exclusive: \u2018Percy Jackson\u2019 Star Dylan Neal Joins as DC\u2019s Dr. Anthony Ivo!|last=Fitzpatrick|first=Kevin|publisher=ScreenCrush|date=September 26, 2013|accessdate=March 9, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306021756/http://screencrush.com/arrow-season-2-dr-anthony-ivo-dylan-neal-exclusive/|archive-date=March 6, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>{{efn|name=\"Note02\"}}\n* [[Jimmy Jean-Louis]] as [[The Captain (Arrowverse)|The Captain]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=48253|title=EXCLUSIVE: \"ARROW\" CASTS JIMMY JEAN-LOUIS AS AMAZO-LINKED \"CAPTAIN\"|last=Phegley|first=Kiel|publisher=Comic Book Resources|date=October 3, 2013|accessdate=October 3, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131003214302/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=48253|archive-date=October 3, 2013|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Nicholas Lea]] as [[Mark Francis (Arrowverse)|Mark Francis]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2013/11/15/arrow-season-2-cast-nicholas-lea-walter-steele-associate/|title=Arrow Exclusive: X-Files Vet Nicholas Lea to Send [Spoiler] on a Surprising Journey|last=Gelman|first=Vlada|publisher=TVLine|date=November 15, 2013|accessdate=November 19, 2013|archive-url=https